24px\"><span style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span style=\"font-size:20px;\"><span style=\"color:rgba(16, 16, 16, 1);\">Established in 1995, Hangzhou Sanyuan Cable Co., Ltd. started as a coaxial cable specialist. Today, Sanyuan has evolved into a comprehensive manufacturer of telecommunications cables, BMS cables, and industrial cables.</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:24px\"><br />\n<span style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span style=\"font-size:20px;\"><span style=\"color:rgba(16, 16, 16, 1);\">We have built a new </span><span style=\"color:rgba(209, 14, 29, 1);\">45,000m&sup2; </span><span style=\"color:rgba(16, 16, 16, 1);\">factory. Equipped with state of the art production lines, it triples our capacity to serve global customers. This enhanced capability helps us offer a wider range of high-quality products, including&nbsp; Lan Cables, Industrial Ethernet Cables, Belden Equivalent Cables, and critical Fire Resistant Cables for safety applications, and more.</span></span></span></p>\n\n", "label": "Established in 1995, Hangzhou Sanyuan Cable Co., Ltd. s", "section": "c_static_001-1762157949289"}, {"key": "about_text_6", "type": "text", "original": "\n        Connectivity Solutions & Reliable Production:\n", "label": "Connectivity Solutions & Reliable Production:", "section": "c_static_001-17622212746450"}, {"key": "about_text_7", "type": "wysiwyg", "original": "\n    <p style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:24px\"><span style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span style=\"font-size:20px;\"><span style=\"color:rgba(16, 16, 16, 1);\">We provide specialized connectivity solutions for diverse sectors. These include Security Cables for alarm and surveillance systems, and robust industrial Cables.</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:24px\"><span style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span style=\"font-size:20px;\"><span style=\"color:rgba(16, 16, 16, 1);\">The latter works for automation, control and data buses in demanding industrial environ