", "original": "\n        The production lines of special cables have been gradually established.\n", "label": "The production lines of special cables have been gradua", "section": "c_static_001-1762237957873"}, {"key": "about_text_47", "type": "text", "original": "\n        2019\n", "label": "2019", "section": "c_static_001-1762237957873"}, {"key": "about_text_48", "type": "text", "original": "\n        2023\n", "label": "2023", "section": "c_static_001-1762237957873"}, {"key": "about_text_49", "type": "text", "original": "\n        A New Era\n", "label": "A New Era", "section": "c_static_001-1762237957873"}, {"key": "about_text_50", "type": "text", "original": "\n        The new factory was officially put into operation, equipped with more production lines and advanced equipment. \n", "label": "The new factory was officially put into operation, equi", "section": "c_static_001-1762237957873"}, {"key": "about_text_51", "type": "text", "original": "\n        SANYUAN coaxial cable was exported overseas.\n", "label": "SANYUAN coaxial cable was exported overseas.", "section": "c_category_302-1765775922043"}, {"key": "about_text_52", "type": "text", "original": "\n        2019\n\n", "label": "2019", "section": "c_category_302-1765775922043"}, {"key": "about_text_53", "type": "wysiwyg", "original": "\n    <p style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"line-height:1.4;\"><strong><span style=\"color:rgba(209, 14, 29, 1);\"><span style=\"font-size:54px;\">Future&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"color:rgba(16, 16, 16, 1);\"><span style=\"font-size:54px;\">Outlook</span></span></strong></span></p>\n\n", "label": "Future Outlook", "section": "c_static_001-17622382811530"}, {"key": "about_text_54", "type": "wysiwyg", "original": "\n    <p style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size:36px;\"><span style=\"line-height:1.4;\"><strong><span style=\"color:rgba(16, 16, 16, 1);\">Shaping the Future of </sp